(10, 6, 'Standardized Public Debt Database | IFD/CMF', 'The availability of valid, comparable, and standardized public debt data is essential for the implementation of sound policies in Latin America and the Caribbean (LAC)', 'This is why at the core of the LAC Debt Group initiative is the development of a standardized sovereign debt database to help debt managers, policy makers, and other actors of financial markets analyze the evolution and composition of public debt in LAC and conduct cross-country comparisons. The information of the database is provided by the public debt offices of LAC countries in response to a questionnaire specifically designed to allow comparability of data. The questionnaire, whose response is non-compulsory, is intended to compile up-to-date standardized statistics for objective and homogeneous definitions of public debt. This update corresponds to the period: II Semester 2006 â€“ I Semester 2015.', '', 'https://mydata.iadb.org/Finance/Standardized-Public-Debt-Database/3bvi-edbq/about ', '2016-04-14 06:30:09', 'See full database'),
(11, 7, '2016 Cybersecurity Report Data Set', 'Cybersecurity: Are we ready in Latin America and the Caribbean?', 'This set comprises the data collected to inform the 2016 Cybersecurity Report, result of the collaboration between the Inter-American Development Bank (IDB), the Organization of American States (OAS), and the Global Cyber Security Capacity Centre (GCSCC) at the University of Oxford. It was collected through an online survey based on the Cybersecurity Capability Maturity Model (CMM) developed by the GCSCC and translated into two languages (English and Spanish). After a piloting stage, the survey was administered to a wide cross-section of national stakeholders in 32 countries in Latin America and the Caribbean. The responses received were aggregated, reviewed, cleaned and complimented with additional sources of information.', '', 'https://mydata.iadb.org/Reform-Modernization-of-the-State/2016-Cybersecurity-Report-Data-Set/cd6z-sjjc', '2016-04-15 08:27:43', 'See full data set'),
(13, 8, 'Finance and Gender Data', 'The Compete Caribbean launched a follow-up survey in Barbados, Jamaica and Trinidad and Tobago', 'This survey on Finance and Gender Issues in the Caribbean (FINGEN) targeted about 400 respondents drawn from the recently completed Latin American and Caribbean Enterprise Surveys (LACES) and aimed to provide feedback from enterprises that participated in the previous round of surveys in 2011 and to capture additional information on firm performance, finance, gender of ownership and management, use of productive development programs, and issues related to management style.\r\n', '', 'https://mydata.iadb.org/Private-Firms-and-SME-Development/Finance-and-Gender-Data/ht9n-748e', '2016-04-28 14:51:06', 'More information'),
(15, 9, 'III EdiciÃ³n de Gobernarte | Premio Eduardo Campos', 'La regiÃ³n avanza en el uso de datos y la identidad legal', 'A fines del mes pasado se realizÃ³ la ceremonia de premiaciÃ³n de la tercera ediciÃ³n de Gobernarte: Premio â€œEduardo Camposâ€, destinada a identificar, reconocer y documentar buenas prÃ¡cticas en el uso de big data y en la mejora de los registros civiles.\r\n\r\nEl presidente Luis Alberto Moreno entregÃ³ los premios a los municipios ganadores de SÃ£o Bernardo do Campo y Fortaleza (Brasil), Antigua Guatemala (Guatemala), Baruta (Venezuela) y Guayaquil (Ecuador). Esta ediciÃ³n, que recordÃ³ al exgobernador de Pernambuco por su gestiÃ³n en la innovaciÃ³n pÃºblica, contÃ³ ademÃ¡s con la especial presencia de su esposa, Renata Campos y sus cinco hijos.\r\n\r\nDurante el evento se presentaron las experiencias ganadoras y hubo un panel por categorÃ­a para conocer mejor cada una de las innovaciones de la boca de sus propios protagonistas. AdemÃ¡s se mostrÃ³ un interactivo para aprender mÃ¡s de cada iniciativa que puedes ver y compartir con tus redes.\r\n\r\nPronto estaremos publicando las notas tÃ©cnicas y difundiendo las bases para el concurso Gobernarte 2016. Mantente informado a travÃ©s de @BID_Gobernarte.', '14634037011.jpg', 'http://www.gobernarte.org/ganadores2015/', '2016-05-16 06:01:41', 'Â¡Mira el interactivo!'),
